name: 奥里亚娜·勒曼
name_full: 奥里亚娜·勒曼 Oriana Leman
birth_place: 蒙特利尔,魁北克,加拿大

last_movies.title: 吉尔莫·德尔·托罗的奇思妙想

introduction: Oriana Leman is a Canadian model, actress, social media star, director, entrepreneur, writer, and TV personality from Montreal, Quebec, Canada. Leman is famously known for her appearance in movies and television series.This girl is an intelligent and creative personality who made her debut in the entertainment industry in the year 2015 by playing a small character in the short movie "Fish Out of Water". Apart from this, Oriana has also worked in many other movies like "The Case That Haunts Me", "I'm Comin' Over", "The Detectives", "Locke & Key", and many others.According to her IMDb, the actress has directed several short movies like "The Whale", "I'm Comin' Over", and others. Leman got a huge fan following through her brilliant acting and modeling skills.
